name: JR Kasprzyk's Repositories
tagline: Open source projects from Joseph Kasprzyk and Patrick Reed
body:
### Introduction
This is a page created to share source code from Joseph Kasprzyk and Patrick Reed's research groups.  Here you can find code from the Lower Rio Grande Valley (LRGV) project and others.

### Authors and Contributors
Also see Jon Herman's page (@jdherman).

### Other Resources
For technical tips and tricks, see our research blog: [Water Programming](http://waterprogramming.wordpress.com)
